<br>
&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp (Rose hits a barrier and is bounced back to the ground.  Hiro runs to Rose to see if she is alright then charges at Akuji.  He is also bounced back.)<br>
<br>
&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp Hiro:&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp He’s too powerful!!<br>
