&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp <br>
&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp (Lena runs up and slashes at him with her daggers.  Akuji grabs one of her daggers and throws her to the ground.  He smiles with satisfaction but when he does a drop of dark blood runs from a cut on his face.  He touches the blood then looks at it.)<br>
<br>
&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp Akuji:&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp Miss Lenexa I presume.<br>
<br>
&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp (Lena looks up at him angrily.  Rose, again, charges at Akuji.  She is thrown away by the barrier, almost without Akuji’s notice.)<br>
<br>
&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp Akuji:&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp Until we meet again, Lenexa.<br>
<br>
&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp (A black portal appears behind him.  He turns to leave through it.)<br>
<br>
&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp Rose:&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp No!  You’re not leaving until we settle the score once and for all!<br>
&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp Akuji:  (smiling) As you wish.<br>
<br>
&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp (Akuji turns around quickly.  Silence.  Hiro mouths the words Rose.<br>
<br>
((//Flash back//))<br>
<br>
&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp (A little girl is crying.<br>
<br>
&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp Young Hiro: What’s the matter?  Why are ya crying??<br>
&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp Deidra:&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp My ball rolled into the forest and I’m lost… (continues to sob.)<br>
