&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp Young Hiro:&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp   (confused) Dee drawn??<br>
&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp Deidra: &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp (laughing) You can call me Rose.  That’s what everyone else calls me.<br>
&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp Young Hiro:&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp  Alright, Rose.  Let’s get ya home.<br>
&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp Deidra:&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp But…<br>
&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp Young Hiro:&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp   Don’t worry!  I’ll protect ya, I promise.<br>
<br>
((//End of Flash back//))<br>
<br>
&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp Hiro:  (faintly) Rose!!<br>
<br>
&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp (Rose opens her eyes to Akuji’s smiling face.)<br>
<br>
&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp Akuji:&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp Now… (stabs her again)<br>
&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp Rose:&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp Ahh!!<br>
<br>
&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp (Behind her, you can see the dagger is all the way through her body.)<br>
<br>
&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp Lena:&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp Rose!!<br>
