<br>
&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp Hiro:&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp NOOooo!!!  Rose!!!! (he falls over her crying)<br>
<br>
