<br>
&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp (A tear falls on the rose.  Hiro looks up with tears going down his face.  The feather floats out of the book and into the wind.  It floats away.)<br>
<br>
&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp Rose:&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp Our love will always go on…&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp <br>
